<module>
    <h>fan</h>
    <p><g>fan</g>
        <vb/>
        <en>stay, remain</en></p>

    <section>
        <h>locations</h>
        <module id="cladach">
            <h>cladach</h>
            <p><g>fan ... aig <a href="?gd=cladach">cladach</a></g>
                <en>... stays at a shore</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Cha do dh’fhan Màiri aig a’ chladach. Ruith i dhachaidh.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary did not stay at the shore. She ran home.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 47</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <module id="taigh">
            <h>taigh</h>
            <p><g>fan ... aig <a href="?gd=taigh">taigh</a></g>
                <en>... stays at a house</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do dh’fhan Màiri aig an taigh an diugh? Cha do dh’fhan. Chaidh Màiri
                            do’n sgoil anns a’ mhadainn</gd>
                        <tr>Did Mary stay at home today? No, she didn’t. She went to school in the
                            morning.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 237–8</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
    </section>

</module>
